name: LGS (Large General Service)
energycomments: Adjustment = Energy Efficiency Rider.  Fixed Monthly Charge = Basic Facilities Charge + Fixed Monthly Leaf 50C Charge.
description: Available to the individual customer with a kilowatt demand of more than 75 kW. If the customer's measured demand is 75 kW or less for twelve consecutive months, the customer will be served under Schedule SGS.
